{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_10_01",
  "title": "赤崎こころ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様、こころ。最近、今まで以上に頑張ってるな\n現場が一緒だった仕事相手の人達も、褒めてたぞ",
      "startTime": 9.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "当然です。こころは謙虚ですから\nBIG4になったからって、調子に乗ったりしません",
      "startTime": 16.7359409015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "偉くなった途端に態度を変えて、評判を下げる\n……そんな小物ムーブ、こころがすると思いますか？",
      "startTime": 23.7359409015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、うん、それもそうだな……\nじゃあ、学校生活の方はどうなんだ？　勉強とか",
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんですか急に。勉強……は、まぁ、それなりです\n大丈夫、じゃないかと思いますよ？　多分……",
      "startTime": 41.5398851395,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "怪しいぞ。BIG4になって仕事が大幅に増えたろ？\n学校に行けない日が増えてるし、気になってな",
      "startTime": 50.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "こころの仕事を\n少しセーブした方がいいんじゃないかと思ってるんだ",
      "startTime": 55.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえいえ！　そんな必要全然ありませんよ\nこころは今、凄く充実してます",
      "startTime": 62.3803430398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "仕事をセーブする必要なんてありません\nむしろ、もっと沢山入れてほしいくらいです！",
      "startTime": 67.6803430398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるよ。だが、アイドルだからといって\n学生としての生活や勉強をおろそかにしないでほしい",
      "startTime": 75.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "学校の試験、もうすぐだろ？\n仕事と学業は両立させないと",
      "startTime": 82,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "ふーん……そんな偉そうなこと言うってことは\n{user}さんにも覚悟はあるんですよね？",
      "startTime": 89.4789830048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え、なんの覚悟だ？",
      "startTime": 92.7628631317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "こころが仕事と学業を両立させるために\n全力でサポートする覚悟、ですよ？",
      "startTime": 98.8791872341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "仕事をセーブして勉強に専念するようでは\n『両立』なんて、言えませんよね～",
      "startTime": 105.4791872341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "なら仕事量は今のままで、{user}さんが\nこころの勉強を見るのが筋ってものじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 112.1125205675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "もっとも、お忙しい{user}さんに\nそんな時間があるとは思えませんけど～？",
      "startTime": 119.2125205675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだな、こころの言う通りだ\nよし、俺と一緒に頑張ろう。ひとまず今度の試験までだ",
      "startTime": 126.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "え。……で、でも、{user}さんだって\nお仕事で忙しいですよね？　無理しなくても……",
      "startTime": 136.3220253626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "仕事の休憩時間と移動時間もフルに使えば\n勉強時間は確保出来るし、後はこころのやる気次第だ",
      "startTime": 144.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "こころのやる気なら、たった今ゼロになりました",
      "startTime": 149.0751700446,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "はは、相変わらず冗談がうまいな、こころは\nそれじゃ、試験に向けて今日から頑張ろう",
      "startTime": 157.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ～？　いきなり今日からですか～？\n……はぁ、余計なこと言っちゃいました",
      "startTime": 165.791881116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "……いや、ポジティブに考えましょう。これなら\n学校に行かなくても、成績をキープ出来るのでは？",
      "startTime": 172.991881116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（学校にもちゃんと行ってもらうんだが……）\n（こころって、そんなに学校が嫌いだったのか……？）",
      "startTime": 180.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『星見フレンドフェス』参加決定後",
      "startTime": 185.1206118589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 186.9206220315
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、例のkanaさんと組んでもらう\n『ニコイチ仲良しユニット決定戦』の件なんだけど……",
      "startTime": 190.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、その節は、ご心配をおかけしました～\n今はkanaさんとこころで、仲良く頑張ってますよ",
      "startTime": 198.2194550511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "私達二人を共演NGにしそうになるくらい\n悩ませちゃったんですよね？　すみませんでした",
      "startTime": 205.7194550511,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "……随分しおらしいな。大体、あんなに嫌がってたのに\nどうして急に組むことになったんだ？",
      "startTime": 214.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "別に何もありませんよ？　ケンカするほど仲がいいって\n言うじゃないですか～。最初のは軽いじゃれ合いですよ",
      "startTime": 221.2886160211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "それにこころはBIG4ですから。元BIG4の\nkanaさんのことくらい、受け止めてあげます",
      "startTime": 231.0886160211,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "……もしかして、狙いは冠番組か？",
      "startTime": 234.5162232285,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr019.m4a",
      "text": "冠番組……？　あ～、優勝したユニットがもらえる\n特典ですよね。それが何か？",
      "startTime": 242.7003169533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "その冠番組が目当てで、無理やり二人で\n仲がいいフリをしてるだけ……なんじゃないのか？",
      "startTime": 248.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr020.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、おかしな{user}さんですね～\n誰だって、冠番組はほしいに決まってるじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 256.9746934092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_10_01-kkr021.m4a",
      "text": "別にkanaさんとこころに限った話じゃないです\nみんなそうじゃないですか？",
      "startTime": 264.9413600758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
